================================================================================
Roboto (bundled fallback font)
================================================================================

This product bundles a subset of the Roboto font (src/shared/slug/fonts/
fallback/roboto.ts, generated from assets/fonts/roboto-fallback.ttf) as a
fallback font for SlugText when no font is otherwise available.

